Upon casting this spell, the priest places <PRO_HISHER>self under a meditative trance.  As long as <PRO_HESHE> continues to meditate, <PRO_HESHE> recieves a +1 bonus to all saves.  However, while <PRO_HESHE> can fight normally, <PRO_HESHE> cannot cast spells, nor turn undead.

