@200001001 = ~Frost Ray~
@200001002 = ~Frost Ray
(Evocation)

Level: Cantrip
Range: Short
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 2-ft. by 40-ft. jet.
Saving Throw: Neg.

Upon casting this spell a ray of ice appears at the caster's fingertips and shoots toward a target of the caster's choice. The ray causes 1d4 points of cold damage to the target to anyone in the ray's path.  Targets can save vs. breath +2 to avoid the ray.

Damage is increased by 1d4, and targets recieve a -1 penalty to their save, at levels 4, 8, 12, 16 and 20.~

@200002001 = ~Jolt~
@200002002 = ~Jolt
(Conjuration/Summoning)

Level: Cantrip
Range: 5'
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: Neg.

Upon casting this spell, the caster generates a jolt of electricty in the body of a nearby enemy. The jolt causes 2d4 points of electical damage, and stops them in their tracks for a crucial 2 seconds if they do not save vs. polymorph +2.

Damage is increased by 1d4 at levels 3, 6, 9, 12, 15 and 18.  Opponents suffer a -1 penalty to their save at levels 10 and 20.

A creature affected by this spell gains immunity to it for one turn as their body retains the electric charge.~

@200003001   = ~Drowse~
@200003002   = ~Drowse

Level: Cantrip
Range: 35'
Duration: 1 round
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: Neg.

This cantrip causes the target to drift off into a very brief slumber, slumping to the ground for 6 seconds before regaining full consciousness.

Opponents receive a -1 penalty to their saves at levels 10 and 20.~
